Today is the anniversary of the death of  Gustav Kirchhoff (1824-1887), German physicist 
\f1\fs28 \cf4 \cb5 who contributed to the fundamental understanding of {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electrical_circuit"}}{\fldrslt \cf6 electrical circuits}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spectroscopy"}}{\fldrslt \cf6 spectroscopy}}, and the emission of {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Black-body"}}{\fldrslt \cf6 black-body}} {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Radiation"}}{\fldrslt \cf6 radiation}} by heated objects.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb5 He coined the term {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Black-body_radiation"}}{\fldrslt \cf6 black-body radiation}} in 1862, and at least two different sets of concepts are named "{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kirchhoff%27s_laws_(disambiguation)"}}{\fldrslt \cf6 Kirchhoff's laws}}" after him, one concerning black body radiation and the other concerning electric circuits.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs32 \cf0 \cb2 With {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://todayinsci.com/3/3_31.htm#BunsenRobert"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 Robert Bunsen}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://chem.ch.huji.ac.il/~eugeniik/history/kirchhoff.htm"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 established}} the theory of spectrum analysis (a technique for chemical analysis by analyzing the light emitted by a heated material), which Kirchhoff applied to determine the composition of the Sun. He found that when light passes through a gas, the gas absorbs those wavelengths that it would emit if heated, which explained the numerous dark lines (Fraunhofer lines) in the Sun's spectrum. \
\
\'c8 oggi l\'92anniversario della morte di  Gustav Kirchhoff \cb2 (1824-1887)\cb2 , fisico tedesco che ha dato contributi fondamentali nella comprensione dei circuiti elettrici, spettroscopia e nell\'92emissione di radiazione da corpo nero. Ha anche coniato il termine \'93corpo nero\'94nel 1862 e almeno due gruppi di regole/concetti che sono oggi chiamate \'93leggi di Kirchhoff\'94.\
